title: Eat Your Veggies - Yo Vegetariano
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Middle Eastern
description: Lunch place offering a menu of the day comprising starter, main, and dessert. Could specifically ask for a vegan version of the menu of the day. Also has burgers, sandwiches, falafel, and other dishes. Reported re-branded Nov 2015 as Eat Your Veggies from its original name Yo Vegetariano.
